 m to  m interested in learning more please contact us to discuss your separation needs and to request a quote watch cerahelix ceo susan mackay’s tedxdirigo talk sign up for updates email address first name last name   required field   cerahelix in the news treat reuse extract create and repeat the circular economy explained using the water cycle as an example plugging into silicon valley from afar cerahelix has been selected to present at the  nrel industry growth forum cerahelix wins the new materials innovation platform pitch contest at plug and play’s expo day         see how the picohelix™ membrane works learn more           interested in using our technology let us help you menu home technology products applications company executive team board of directors news contact us cerahelix inc private company information  bloomberg july    pm et machinery company overview of cerahelix inc snapshot people company overview cerahelix inc designs and manufactures picohelix ceramic membrane products to make products from biomass reuse and recycle resources and to purify water it offers single channel elements for lab scale and small pilot scale studies and multichannel elements for commercial scale projects the company also provides filter element housings for individual and multielement configurations and sells and leases laboratory test systems for small scale research and development testing needs it serves treatment separation and laboratory applications the company was founded in  and is based in orono maine  godfrey driveorono me united statesfounded in  phone  fax  wwwcerahelixcom key executives for cerahelix inc ms susan g mackay chairman of the board ceo  president mr donald mackay chief financial officer ms jutta von dirke vice president of business strategy mr james v banks vp of applications engineering  director mr karl bishop chief scientific officer compensation as of fiscal year  similar private companies by industry company name region vantage corporation